  "title": "Microbiology (MNC) #HMS",
  "description": "<p><strong> $2.6K to $2.7K</strong><br /><strong>1 year contract </strong><br />Office hours, Mon to Fri<br />Location at Biopolis, Buona Vista <br />After 1 year, can convert  </p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform routine and non-routine microbiological testing as part of R&D studies.</li><li>Preparation of media, perform sample plating, incubation and colony enumeration.</li><li>Handle and maintain laboratory equipment, ensuring it is calibrated and functioning</li><li>Document results in Electronic Lab Notebook (ELN) and upload data into the LIMS system</li><li>Maintain lab cleanliness and manage lab supplies to ensure a well-organized and efficient work</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p></p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p><p></p>",
